<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to ${MallName}!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .email-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #1e90ff;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #1e90ff;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        a {
            color: #1e90ff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #ffa500;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
        Welcome to ${MallName}!
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Dear ${CustomerName},</h2>
        <p>üéâ Congratulations! üéà You've just unlocked a world of exclusive shopping delights by creating an account with us at ${MallName}. We're thrilled to have you on board!</p>
