        <p>Should you need any assistance or have a question, our customer service wizards are always ready to cast a helpful spell. Just reach out to [customer service email/contact information].</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing ${MallName}. We're looking forward to making your shopping experience extraordinary. Happy shopping!</p>
        <p>Best wishes,</p>
        <p>The ${MallName} Team</p>
